00:01:05.240 --> 00:01:07.710
Okay, so today what we're going to
be talking about is developing

00:01:07.910 --> 00:01:11.720
for Mac OS X Managed Desktop.

00:01:12.870 --> 00:01:16.930
Mac OS X is a managed environment,
and we're going to be discussing

00:01:17.590 --> 00:01:21.180
in a variety of ways how it
