00:01:25.330 --> 00:01:27.300
concept of Apple desktop management.

00:01:27.300 --> 00:01:29.300
And it's a year later.

00:01:29.300 --> 00:01:31.300
We've got a year's worth
of software under our belt.

00:01:31.300 --> 00:01:35.770
We've got customers who are
